							<div class="hint">What is the customer trying to get done? Functional, social, and emotional jobs.</div>
							<div class="field"><input type="text" id="vp-job-1" maxlength="100" placeholder="Job 1: e.g., Report channel ROI to the CFO every quarter" /></div>
							<div class="field"><input type="text" id="vp-job-2" maxlength="100" placeholder="Job 2: e.g., Decide how to reallocate budget across paid + organic" /></div>
							<div class="field"><input type="text" id="vp-job-3" maxlength="100" placeholder="Job 3: e.g., Defend marketing as a profit center, not cost" /></div>
							<div class="field"><input type="text" id="vp-job-4" maxlength="100" placeholder="Job 4 (optional): e.g., Align with sales on lead-source quality" /></div>
						</fieldset>

						<fieldset data-section-card="vp-pains-card">
							<legend>3. Customer pains<label class="section-toggle"><input type="checkbox" class="section-toggle-input" data-toggle-card="vp-pains-card" checked /><span class="section-toggle-track"></span></label></legend>
							<div class="hint">What frustrates them today? Costs, blockers, risks, undesired outcomes.</div>
							<div class="field"><input type="text" id="vp-pain-1" maxlength="100" placeholder="Pain 1: e.g., Manual attribution takes 3 days every quarter" /></div>
							<div class="field"><input type="text" id="vp-pain-2" maxlength="100" placeholder="Pain 2: e.g., Can't trust the numbers when the CFO asks" /></div>
							<div class="field"><input type="text" id="vp-pain-3" maxlength="100" placeholder="Pain 3: e.g., Engineering won't prioritize new tracking" /></div>
